   <shortdesc>The phrase (&lt;<keyword>ph</keyword>&gt;) element is used to organize content
for reuse or conditional processing (for example, when part of a paragraph
applies to a particular audience). It can be used by future specializations
of DITA to apply specific processing or formatting to marked up phrases.</shortdesc>
